OL,5, A former Scottish council leader has   
OL,6, been charged in connection with an     
OL,7, alleged romance fraud.                 
OL,9,FEast Dunbartonshire councillor, Andrew 
OL,10,FPolson, 50, was previously named in a  
OL,11,Fseparate civil court action by a woman 
OL,12,Fwho claimed he had breached her trust. 
OL,14,FIn legal papers, the woman, 68, said Mr
OL,15,FPolson had persuaded her to let him    
OL,16,Fmanage her finances and used her money 
OL,17,Fto buy property for himself.           
OL,19,FHe was suspended by the Scottish       
OL,20,FConservative party in June.            
